Work_Description:
Walmart are proposing exterior colour and signage modifications related to the new corporate colours and a new Online PickUp entrance on the west side of the building.  The modifications are within the existing building footprint and no new GFA is being proposed.
The modifications include:
Add directional OMNI (Online) orange + Signage on building; 
Add Online Pickup entrance on west side of building;
New building signage and paint on all exterior facades;
Relocate the existing on-line parking stalls from the front of the store to west side of the building.   There is no loss of parking as a result.   
Interior renovations to accommodate new Online pickup area and various department improvements.
